title: Must See: Efficiency - Studio updated w/tile in Lauderhill
posting_body: ['Kings Row Apartments.', 'Very nice updated studio for only $1200 a month, Full tile throughout the unit,  very big bathroom with closet inside.', 'Full new kitchen with stove, refrigerator and sink with granite counter-top, central AC and impact windows.', 'Laundry facility on site.', 'On site maintenance team, very fast turnaround.', 'On site cameras and security system, a great addition.', '1 assigned parking spot.', 'Tile throughout, shows very nicely.', 'Just a few minutes drive from the turnpike, ideal location in Lauderhill.', 'Perfect place for anyone looking for an affordable studio in a convenient location.', '*Water is included in rent!!', '**Electric and cable is billed to tenant.', '1 hour application turnaround available..', '**MUST HAVE MINIMUM OF $2700 MONTHLY INCOME', 'First month, and one and a half month security deposit required, with background checks for all residents over 18 years of age.', '$3000 to move in,', 'No association to approve or deny.', 'Pets welcome with refundable deposit.', 'Private owner of rental building.', 'These images may or may not be the actual unit, but all units are similar in upgrades.']
